title: ??? where's my victorious skin
body: I received Maokai but i didn't receive the skin? Lol also received the icon and border

replies.body: thanks for the update ^(o.o^) im in this boat too

I know a few summoners here have reported that they've received most of their rewards but  Victorious Maokai is missing. ** Don't worry!**  

If you've received most of your Gold+ reward but don't have your skin yet, it's on the way and there is nothing wrong with your account.  Rest easy knowing that we're still distributing the rewards, and you'll be showing off your Victorious skin as soon as we're wrapped up.  Per the[ Season 6 FAQ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/2016-ranked-season-ends-soon), we aim to be done by the 21st but some may see them sooner than others.  

Brace yourself, they are coming!
D: sad life i wanted to show it off
